2032	  // Version of initialize_workspace that takes in as input the number of CTAs in the M and N dimensions.
2033	  // This is useful for calculating the tiled shape when a mode of problem and/or CTA shape has rank > 1,
2034	  // for which using CuTe algebra for calculating tile shapes is easiest.
